snippet.title: MTV Celebrity Ex On The Beach UK
snippet.description:
What happens when eight smoking hot single guys and girls arrive in paradise for a dream holiday of sun, sea, sex and good times? If only life were that simple. Because just as things get off to a sizzling start, MTV brings in their exes to break up the party - one by one! As the eight original singles are left wondering "whose Ex is next?", trouble in paradise thickens as love triangles become tangled webs of lust, love and loathing. 

Follow along and make sure to subscribe to the official MTV Celebrity Ex On The Beach UK YouTube channel for all the latest sneak peeks and full episodes!
